Erebot v0.3.0
-------------

The code underwent some serious changes. Most notably, events have been
rewritten from the grounds up.

Changelog:
*   Added glob-like XInclude processing in configuration files [#267]
*   Created the PLOP sub-project which deals with centralized logging [147]
*   Allowed configurations to be loaded from a string (helps tests) [#200]
*   Split events in different classes [#151]
*   Added support for the STARTTLS extension [#69]
*   Added more tests [#67]
*   some other minor changes

